	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">The First Day</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From The Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead Wiki</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><div class="mw-revision"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 01:36, 9 March 2023 by <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=User:Nc4me&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-userlink" title="User:Nc4me (page does not exist)"><bdi>Nc4me</bdi></a> <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=User_talk:Nc4me&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-usertoollinks-talk" title="User talk:Nc4me (page does not exist)">talk</a> | <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/Special:Contributions/Nc4me" class="mw-usertoollinks-contribs" title="Special:Contributions/Nc4me">contribs</a>)</span> <span class="comment">(improve Arrival (slightly))</span></div><div id="mw-revision-nav">(<a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=The_First_Day&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=40653" title="The First Day">diff</a>) <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php?title=The_First_Day&amp;direction=prev&amp;oldid=40653" title="The First Day">← Older revision</a> | Latest revision (diff) | Newer revision → (diff)</div></div></div>
		
		
		
